OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FThe First Minister has been accused of
OL,7,F"massaging" the figures when it comes
OL,8,Fto the numbers of apprenticeships
OL,9,Fcreated here in Wales.
OL,11,FBut Eluned Morgan hit back at Plaid
OL,12,FCymru claims that the totals included
OL,13,Fthose who dropped out of
OL,14,Fapprenticeship courses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]
