OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FIt came in a clash during the weekly
OL,7,FFirst Minister's Question session when
OL,8,Fthe Plaid Cymru leader highlighted
OL,9,FLabour claims that it has hit its
OL,10,Ftarget of the number of
OL,11,Fapprenticeships it has overseen during
OL,12,Fthe five years that it's been in
OL,13,Fcharge of the Welsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FRhun ap Iorwerth said that its claim
OL,7,Fwas based on a misleading use of
OL,8,Fstatistics. He said that when it comes
OL,9,Fto adding up the number of
OL,10,Fapprenticeships, "You don't count them
OL,11,Funtil an apprentice has completed
OL,12,Feight weeks. You don't measure those
OL,13,Fdropping out before, because you're
OL,14,Flooking for positive and successful
OL,15,Foutcomes."
OL,26,@rD@ROUwD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FHe said that official figures using
OL,7,Fthat method showed that "there had
OL,8,Fbeen just over 91,000 apprenticeships
OL,9,Fdelivered during this Senedd term.
OL,10,FThen, a few weeks later, on 10
OL,11,FFebruary, the Minister for Skills
OL,12,Fannounced in the Chamber that the
OL,13,FWelsh Government had, and I quote,
OL,14,Fachieved its target of having
OL,15,Fdelivered 100,000 apprenticeships.
OL,26,@oD@YOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,F"Now, setting aside the fact that the
OL,7,Foriginal target was 125,000, now
OL,8,Freduced by 25,000 apprentices, will
OL,9,Fthe First Minister confirm that the
OL,10,F100,000 figure has, in fact, only been
OL,11,Fachieved by using a far less rigorous
OL,12,Fmeasure, where the Government does now
OL,13,Finclude those who have dropped out
OL,14,Fearly?"
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, sent direct
OL,19,Fto your inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@GO]
