OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FIn response to the Plaid Cymru
OL,7,Fleaders's claims, Eluend Morgan said
OL,8,Fthat "We've got a system that has been
OL,9,Ftried and tested and understood, and
OL,10,FI'm not ashamed of getting people from
OL,11,Foutside of Wales to come and kick the
OL,12,Ftyres on what we're doing."
OL,14,FAnd she said that "we have hit the
OL,15,Ftarget of 100,000 apprenticeships.
OL,16,FThat's something that I think we
OL,17,Fshould be very proud of."
OL,26,@pD@FOUtD@[O]vD@SOUyD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
