PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FDarren Millar said that "For every #1
OL,7,Fspent per head on a patient in
OL,8,FEngland, Wales gets #1.20 to spend
OL,9,Fhere. You have enough money to spend
OL,10,Ftens of millions of pounds on changing
OL,11,F20 mph zones across our country, you
OL,12,Fspend tens of millions on an airport
OL,13,Fthat you don't need to invest in and
OL,14,Fyou're prepared to spend #120 million
OL,15,Fon more politicians. You cannot make
OL,16,Fthese arguments about money when
OL,17,Fyou're spending in that wasteful sort
OL,18,Fof way."
OL,26,@nD@YOUzD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
