CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,FIn response, the First Minister said
OL,7,Fthat "Today, we're able to put more
OL,8,Fmoney into the health service, thanks
OL,9,Fto the additional funding we've had,
OL,10,Fbecause the taps have now been turned
OL,11,Fback on.
OL,26,@oD@FOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
