OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1771970741
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'massaging'
OL,4,Capprenticeship figures
OL,6,F"And that's why we're celebrating the
OL,7,Ffact that for the seventh month in a
OL,8,Frow, waiting lists are coming down.
OL,9,FThe number of people waiting for
OL,10,Ftreatment is the lowest in three
OL,11,Fyears, and the longest waiting lists
OL,12,Fhave come down by 92 per cent since
OL,13,Fthe peak. The average waiting time in
OL,14,FWales is 19 weeks. Do we want to
OL,15,Fimprove on that? Absolutely. But we're
OL,16,Fabsolutely heading in the right
OL,17,Fdirection."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@KO]
